thread.title: Adriana Conder

author: Adriana Conder
title: Adriana Conder
text: I ordered my wedding invitations through Optimal-print and i cannot recommend them enough. Their designs are wonderful and high quality and their prices are great. I received exactly what i ordered and the shipping time was great. Much better service than other popular competitors. Thank you so much for making this part of the wedding planning as simple and stress-free as possible!
